      "body": "I'm not sure we can make this change. It seems `PSBT_GLOBAL_VERSION` is a different key on each version.\n\nDo you know why the name of the field is the same in both BIPs, but for BIP 370 the keytype for `PSBT_GLOBAL_VERSION` is `0x02` and for BIP 174 the `PSBT_GLOBAL_VERSION` keytype is `0xFB`? What are we missing here?",
